<nav class="nav" id="nav" data-screen-label="Nav"><svg class="sunmark" viewBox="0 0 32 32" aria-hidden="true"><circle class="sun-disc" cx="16" cy="16" r="10"></circle></svg><a class="wm" href="/">AMPM <small>BUILDING SERVICES</small></a><div class="links"><a href="/services/" class="">Services</a><a href="/work/" class="">Work</a><a href="/compliance/" class="">Compliance</a><a href="/about/" class="">About</a><a href="/contact/" class="">Contact</a></div><a class="phone" href="tel:03300430080">0330 043 0080</a></nav><div class="page" style="--svc: var(--m-blue);"><div class="shell"><section class="sec p-hero"><div class="reveal in"><span class="svc-bar" style="background: var(--m-blue);"></span></div><div class="reveal in"><div class="kicker">Services · 04</div></div><h1 class="reveal d1 in">Landscaping &amp; External Works</h1><p class="lede reveal d2 in">The external environment around the building — hard and soft landscaping, surfacing, boundaries and finishes that make a completed building look finished. Delivered alongside the trades inside, so <strong>handover is the whole site, not just the shell.</strong></p><div class="reveal d3 in" style="margin-top: 28px;"><a class="btn line sm" href="/contact/">Enquire about groundworks →</a></div></section><section class="sec tight"><div class="reveal in" style="margin-bottom: 32px;"><div class="kicker">What we deliver</div><h2 class="dhead sm">The full external scope,<br>self-delivered.</h2></div><div class="capgroups reveal in"><div class="capgroup"><h4><span class="dot" style="background: var(--m-blue);"></span><span><a href="/groundworks/hard-landscaping/" style="color:inherit;text-decoration:underline;text-underline-offset:3px;text-decoration-thickness:2px;">Hard landscaping</a></span></h4><ul><li>Paving, paths &amp; patios</li><li>Block, flag &amp; resin surfaces</li><li>Steps, ramps &amp; retaining</li><li>Decking &amp; terraces</li></ul></div><div class="capgroup"><h4><span class="dot" style="background: var(--m-blue);"></span><span><a href="/groundworks/soft-landscaping/" style="color:inherit;text-decoration:underline;text-underline-offset:3px;text-decoration-thickness:2px;">Soft landscaping</a></span></h4><ul><li>Planting, beds &amp; turfing</li><li>Topsoil &amp; ground prep</li><li>Trees, hedging &amp; screening</li><li>Irrigation &amp; establishment</li></ul></div><div class="capgroup"><h4><span class="dot" style="background: var(--m-blue);"></span><span><a href="/groundworks/surfacing/" style="color:inherit;text-decoration:underline;text-underline-offset:3px;text-decoration-thickness:2px;">Surfacing &amp; access</a></span></h4><ul><li>Car parks &amp; hardstanding</li><li>Roads, footpaths &amp; cycleways</li><li>Permeable paving &amp; drainage</li><li>Line marking &amp; signage</li></ul></div><div class="capgroup"><h4><span class="dot" style="background: var(--m-blue);"></span><span><a href="/groundworks/boundaries/" style="color:inherit;text-decoration:underline;text-underline-offset:3px;text-decoration-thickness:2px;">Boundaries &amp; features</a></span></h4><ul><li>Walls, fencing &amp; gates</li><li>Railings &amp; balustrades</li><li>Kerbing &amp; edgings</li><li>Street furniture &amp; lighting</li></ul></div></div></section><section class="sec tight"><div class="reveal in" style="margin-bottom: 32px;"><div class="kicker">How we work</div><h2 class="dhead sm">From levels to handover —<br>and beyond.</h2></div><ol class="steps reveal in"><li class="step"><span class="step-n">01</span><div><h4>Survey &amp; setting-out</h4><p>We survey the existing ground, take levels and set out the scheme — confirming falls, drainage runs and tie-ins before a spade goes in, so the finished levels work first time.</p></div></li><li class="step"><span class="step-n">02</span><div><h4>Design &amp; specification</h4><p>We develop a landscape architect’s design through to construction, or specify the package ourselves — materials, build-ups and detailing chosen to meet the brief, the budget and the standards.</p></div></li><li class="step"><span class="step-n">03</span><div><h4>Ground prep &amp; sub-bases</h4><p>Excavation, formation, sub-bases and edge restraints — the unseen work that decides whether paving and surfacing last. Built to BS 7533, with permeable build-ups where SuDS demands them.</p></div></li><li class="step"><span class="step-n">04</span><div><h4>Hard landscaping &amp; surfacing</h4><p>Paving, surfacing, kerbing, walls, fencing and street furniture self-delivered by our own teams — sequenced around the trades inside so the external package never holds up handover.</p></div></li><li class="step"><span class="step-n">05</span><div><h4>Soft landscaping &amp; handover</h4><p>Topsoil, planting, turf and trees installed to BS 4428, then an establishment period to nurse the planting in — followed by a clean handover with maintenance records and as-builts.</p></div></li></ol></section><section class="sec tight"><div class="reveal in" style="margin-bottom: 32px;"><div class="kicker">Standards &amp; compliance</div><h2 class="dhead sm">Built to the codes that<br>last outside.</h2></div><div class="capgroups reveal in"><div class="capgroup"><h4><span class="dot" style="background: var(--m-blue);"></span><span>The standards we build to</span></h4><ul><li>BS 7533 — paving &amp; block surfacing</li><li>BS 8500 — concrete specification</li><li>BS 4428 &amp; BS 5837 — soft landscaping &amp; trees near construction</li><li>BS 1722 — fencing systems</li><li>CIRIA SuDS Manual (C753) &amp; Building Regs Part M</li><li>CDM 2015 across every package</li></ul></div><div class="capgroup"><h4><span class="dot" style="background: var(--m-blue);"></span><span>Backed by AMPM Group</span></h4><ul><li>The Group’s accreditations behind every job</li><li>29 years of group trading history, since 1997</li><li>One project manager accountable per programme</li><li>Coordinated as the final external package on fit-out, refurb &amp; new-build</li><li>PQQ and reference packs on request</li></ul></div></div></section><section class="sec tight"><div class="reveal in" style="margin-bottom: 28px;"><div class="kicker">Sectors</div><h2 class="dhead sm">Where external works<br>finish the job.</h2></div><div class="sectorrow reveal in"><span class="sector">Commercial &amp; public realm</span><span class="sector">Residential &amp; BTR</span><span class="sector">Education</span><span class="sector">Healthcare</span><span class="sector">Industrial &amp; logistics</span><span class="sector">Retail</span><span class="sector">Hospitality</span><span class="sector">Public sector</span></div><p class="body" style="margin-top:22px;max-width:60ch;">We deliver landscaping and external-works packages across London and the South East — including Sussex, Surrey, Kent, Hampshire and Berkshire — for direct clients, Tier-1 main contractors and blue-chip FM providers.</p></section><section class="sec tight"><div class="intro2 reveal in"><div><div class="kicker">Market drivers</div><h2 class="dhead sm">Where the work<br>is coming from.</h2></div><p class="body">External completion and landscaping packages on fit-out, refurbishment and new-build schemes — the works that turn a finished building into a finished site.</p></div></section><section class="sec"><div class="reveal in" style="margin-bottom: 32px;"><div class="kicker">Representative projects</div><h2 class="dhead sm">Groundworks work, in the field.</h2></div><div class="caselist reveal in"><div class="case-card"><img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1581094794329-c8112a89af12?auto=format&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=900&amp;q=75" alt="Landscaping &amp; external works project — South East" loading="lazy" style="width: 100%; height: 200px; display: block; object-fit:cover;" /><span class="ctag" style="background: var(--m-blue); position: absolute;">Groundworks · Landscaping</span><h4>Public realm — London</h4><p class="cs">Hard and soft landscaping to the external public realm of a commercial building.</p><div class="cm"><div><div class="k">Value</div><div class="v">£1.9m</div></div><div><div class="k">Programme</div><div class="v">24 wks</div></div></div></div><div class="case-card"><img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1517089152318-42ec560349c0?auto=format&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=900&amp;q=75" alt="Landscaping &amp; external works project — South East" loading="lazy" style="width: 100%; height: 200px; display: block; object-fit:cover;" /><span class="ctag" style="background: var(--m-blue); position: absolute;">Groundworks · Hard landscaping</span><h4>Courtyard — Surrey</h4><p class="cs">Paving, planting and boundary works to a refurbished office courtyard.</p><div class="cm"><div><div class="k">Value</div><div class="v">£760k</div></div><div><div class="k">Programme</div><div class="v">15 wks</div></div></div></div><div class="case-card"><img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1487958449943-2429e8be8625?auto=format&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=900&amp;q=75" alt="Landscaping &amp; external works project — South East" loading="lazy" style="width: 100%; height: 200px; display: block; object-fit:cover;" /><span class="ctag" style="background: var(--m-blue); position: absolute;">Groundworks · Surfacing</span><h4>Car park — Kent</h4><p class="cs">Surfacing, kerbing and external finishes to a refreshed car park and approach.</p><div class="cm"><div><div class="k">Value</div><div class="v">£590k</div></div><div><div class="k">Programme</div><div class="v">13 wks</div></div></div></div></div><p class="case-note">Representative of the Groundworks work we are set up to deliver. Named, full-format case studies follow as projects complete — PQQ references available on request.</p></section><section class="sec tight"><div class="reveal in" style="margin-bottom: 28px;"><div class="kicker">FAQs</div><h2 class="dhead sm">External-works questions,<br>answered.</h2></div><div class="faq reveal in"><details class="faq-item"><summary>Do you cover both hard and soft landscaping?</summary><p>Yes. We self-deliver the full external scope — paving, surfacing, kerbing, walls, fencing and street furniture on the hard side, and topsoil, planting, turf and trees on the soft side — as one coordinated package to BS 7533 and BS 4428.</p></details><details class="faq-item"><summary>Do you handle external drainage, SuDS and permeable paving?</summary><p>Yes. We design and build surface-water drainage as part of the external works — including permeable paving and SuDS features detailed to the CIRIA SuDS Manual (C753) — so the surfacing and the drainage are delivered by one team.</p></details><details class="faq-item"><summary>Do you maintain planting after install?</summary><p>Yes. New planting and turf are installed to BS 4428, then carried through a defined establishment period — watering, weeding, replacement of failures and care of trees set out to BS 5837 — so the soft landscaping is established, not just planted, at handover.</p></details><details class="faq-item"><summary>Can you work on occupied or live sites?</summary><p>Yes. Much of our external work is phased around live, occupied buildings — out-of-hours access, segregated routes and protected pedestrian flows under CDM 2015 — so the site stays open while we work.</p></details><details class="faq-item"><summary>Do you help with biodiversity net gain and planning landscape conditions?</summary><p>Yes. We deliver the landscape works that discharge planning conditions and support biodiversity net-gain commitments — native planting, habitat features and the records to evidence them — alongside the landscape architect and ecologist where one is appointed.</p></details><details class="faq-item"><summary>Which areas do you cover?</summary><p>We deliver landscaping and external works across London and the South East, including Sussex, Surrey, Kent, Hampshire and Berkshire. Send us the site address and we’ll arrange a survey.</p></details></div></section><section class="sec tight line-top xlinks" data-xlink><div class="reveal in" style="margin-bottom: 22px;"><div class="kicker">Explore more</div><h2 class="dhead sm">Related across<br>AMPM Building&nbsp;Services.</h2></div><div class="xgroup reveal in"><span class="xlabel">Areas we cover</span><div class="sectorrow"><a class="sector" href="/areas/london/">London</a><a class="sector" href="/areas/crawley-gatwick/">Crawley &amp; Gatwick</a><a class="sector" href="/areas/brighton-hove/">Brighton &amp; Hove</a><a class="sector" href="/areas/guildford-surrey/">Guildford &amp; Surrey</a></div></div><div class="xgroup reveal in"><span class="xlabel">Sectors we serve</span><div class="sectorrow"><a class="sector" href="/sectors/offices/">Commercial Offices</a><a class="sector" href="/sectors/healthcare/">Healthcare</a><a class="sector" href="/sectors/industrial/">Industrial &amp; Logistics</a><a class="sector" href="/sectors/residential/">Residential &amp; BTR</a><a class="sector" href="/sectors/">All sectors →</a></div></div></section><section class="sec tight line-top"><div class="reveal in" style="margin-bottom: 24px;"><div class="kicker">The other three lines</div><h2 class="dhead sm">One contractor,<br>four service lines.</h2></div><div class="otherlines reveal in"><a class="otherline" href="/meph/"><span class="ol-l"><span class="ol-sw" style="background: var(--m-green);"></span><span class="ol-nm">MEPH</span></span><span class="ol-go">→</span></a><a class="otherline" href="/commercial/"><span class="ol-l"><span class="ol-sw" style="background: var(--m-purple);"></span><span class="ol-nm">Commercial</span></span><span class="ol-go">→</span></a><a class="otherline" href="/fabric/"><span class="ol-l"><span class="ol-sw" style="background: var(--m-orange);"></span><span class="ol-nm">Fabric</span></span><span class="ol-go">→</span></a></div></section></div><section class="band" data-nav-dark="true" style="background: var(--m-blue); color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><div class="shell"><div class="cta-split reveal in"><div><div class="k